snippet.title: Angry Birds Go! Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to downhill racing on Piggy Island! Download Angry Birds Go! http://rov.io/downloadABgo

In the NEW Angry Birds Go! launch trailer, see those birds and piggies go head-to-head in a fast and furious race to the finish line!

Angry Birds Go! races into app stores worldwide and is now available to download for iOS, Android devices, Windows Phone 8 and Blackberry 10!

LIKE Angry Birds at http://facebook.com/angrybirds
FOLLOW Angry Birds at http://twitter.com/angrybirds
SUBMIT fan art at http://angrybirds.tumblr.com
